AS INTRODUCED
6
7
An Act relating to investment accounts; creating the
7
Oklahoma Dream Accounts Investment Program Act;
8
providing short title; defining terms; creating the
8
Oklahoma Dream Account Investment Program;
9
authorizing one-time contributions to certain Trump
9
Accounts; requiring verification; making
10
contributions subject to availability of funds;
10
prescribing order of contributions; requiring the
11
State Treasurer to prescribe form; authorizing State
11
Treasurer to promulgate rules; providing construing
12
provisions; creating the Oklahoma Trump Account
12
Investment Fund; providing for deposits to fund;
13
providing for expenditures from fund; providing for
13
